ime) - Seeker is a guy<BR>* Kill Plasmatic Priest<BR>* Loot "Blood Soaked Plasmatic Priest Robe"<P>* Go to Solusek A<BR>* Go the room has pit in it loc (-796, -366)<BR>* Kill Lord Gimblox - 19 min. spawn, PH "Lg Fire Goblin" or "fire goblin shaman"<BR>* Loot "Lord Gimblox's Signet Ring"<P>* Go to Timorous Deep<BR>* Go to Island loc (-11567, -2227)<BR>* Swim through cave entrance at loc (-11530, -3728)<BR>* Swim to the other side<BR>* Head right keeping the on your left<BR>* Swim through the other cave entrance at (-11336, -1307<BR>* Enter the Hidden Oasis<BR>* Find Omat Vastsea on Pier<BR>* Give Omat "Blood Soaked Plasmatic Priest Robe" <BR>* Receive "Orb of Frozen Water" <BR>* Find Natasha Whitewater in building behind Omat<BR>* Give "Lord Gimblox's Signet Ring" to Natasha Whitewater<BR>* Receive "Ornate Sea Shell (II)"<P>Step Two: Obtain the Orb of Clear Water<BR>* Go to Burning Woods<BR>* Give "Ornate Sea Shell (II)" to Naxot Deepwater loc (3400, -2150)<BR>* Receive "Message to Natasha".<BR>* Kill Ixiblat Fer<BR>* Loot "Sceptre of Ixiblat Fer"<P>* Go to Chardok<BR>* Kill Overking Bathezid Di'Zok<BR>* Loot "Singed Scroll"<P>* Go to Timorous Deep<BR>* Go to Island loc (-11567, -2227)<BR>* Swim through cave entrance at loc (-11530, -3728)<BR>* Swim to the other side<BR>* Head right keeping the on your left<BR>* Swim through the other cave entrance at (-11336, -1307<BR>* Enter the Hidden Oasis<BR>* Find Omat Vastsea on Pier<BR>* Give "Sceptre of Ixiblat Fer" and "Singed Scroll" to Omat Vastsea<BR>* Receive "Orb of Clear Water"<BR>* Find Natasha Whitewater in building behind Omat<BR>* Give "Message to Natasha" to Natasha Whitewater<BR>* Receive "Shimmering Pearl"<P>Step Three: Obtain the Orb of Vapor <BR>* Go to Nagafen’s Lair<BR>* Go towards the Fire Giants Castle<BR>* Across the ramp there is a ledge Under that banner, Zordak Ragefire will spawn<BR>* Give "Shimmering Pearl" to Zordak Ragefire<BR>* Receive "Swirling Pearl"<P>* Go to Skyfire Mountains<BR>* Go to LOC p3200 n3200 - Big Dragon statue, he spawns in front <BR>* Kill Zordak Ragefire, the human level 55<BR>* Kill Zordakalicus Ragefire, Dragon Level 60<BR>* Loot "Impure Heart of Ragefire" NO DROP Container<BR>* Place the "Swirling Pearl" inside Heart<BR>* Click Combine, Container becomes " Heart of Ragefire" <P>* Go to Timorous Deep<BR>* Go to Island loc (-11567, -2227)<BR>* Swim through cave entrance at loc (-11530, -3728)<BR>* Swim to the other side<BR>* Head right keeping the on your left<BR>* Swim through the other cave entrance at (-11336, -1307<BR>* Enter the Hidden Oasis<BR>* Find Omat Vastsea on Pier<BR>* Give "Heart of Zordak Ragefire" to Omat Vastsea<BR>* Receive "Orb of Vapor"<P>Step Four: Obtain the Orb of the Triumvirate<BR>* Find Jhassad Oceanson on the beach by a tree<BR>* Give "Orb of Frozen Water", "Orb of Clear Water", <BR>and "Orb of Vapor" to Jhassad Oceanson<P>Step Five: Obtain the Water Sprinkler of Nem Ankh<BR>* Be patient, Avatar of Water end up beside Jhassad<BR>* Give "Orb of the Triumvirate" to Avatar of Water<BR>* Receiving the Water Sprinkler of Nem Ankh<P><p>[This message has been edited by ShelseaDruid (edited 04-24-2002).]</FONT></TD></TR><TR bgcolor="#f7f7f7"><TD valign=top><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">leonnesizetetic</FONT></TD><TD><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">Thank you, Thank you, Thank you.  Someone really should tell Allakhazam that his information is dated (someone that has verified the information).<P>------------------<BR>Leonne si`Zetetic<BR>Officer of the Arcane Guardians<BR>Innoruuk Server</FONT></TD></TR><TR bgcolor="#dedfdf"><TD valign=top><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">fournot</FONT></TD><TD><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">Bump to keep this up top<P> Yes yes  Shameless but it should stay there.<BR></FONT></TD></TR><TR bgcolor="#f7f7f7"><TD valign=top><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">Daynan</FONT></TD><TD><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">Oops you got it wrong!<P>STEP 1<BR>* Go to Skyfire Mou