n in mob (like the druid epic) that would make it alot more sense IMO.  <P>All the chance that Verant did was to MAKE THINGS WORSE, it was a contested spawn before but now its even worse, no disrespect but killing Rage at the beginning of the epic just makes things harder for the other poor clerics that have completed their epic apart from Rage.<P>We have a list in force on Rodcet Nife which seems to be working ok but im way down the list (19th) I just hope all of those in front of me have completed their epic (apart from Rage) because I think its unfair to make us clerics that have done everything else wait any longer than we have waited already.  <P>just my 2 cents....<P>Alilinkie<BR>59 cleric<BR>Rodcet Nife</FONT></TD></TR><TR bgcolor="#dedfdf"><TD valign=top><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">Daynan</FONT></TD><TD><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">Sorry wasn't blaming you ShelseaDruid. <P>You didn't get it wrong. Verant got it wrong.</FONT></TD></TR><TR bgcolor="#f7f7f7"><TD valign=top><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">ShelseaDruid</FONT></TD><TD><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial"> <BLOCKQUOTE><font size="1" face="Verdana, Arial">quote:</font><HR>Originally posted by ShelseaDruid:<BR><B>Thanks for those who helped me fix this<P>CHECK OFF LIST<BR>ITEMS NEEDED<BR>Some form of Enduring Breath<BR>Rations & Water as camping take awhile<BR>Lots of friends for the big fights<P>Step One: Obtain the Orb of Frozen Water<BR>* Go to Lake Rathetear<BR>* Go to Island with 3 Aviaks loc (2800, 150) <BR>* Swim under Island<BR>* Go to cave entrance loc (2831, -912, -221)<BR>* Go to Aquagoblin Tower (note: Wolfform = no aggro)<BR>* Kill all 4 Aquagoblin on top of tower - Do not use AE – Deep is tough<BR>* Kill Lord Begurgle in Lake Rathe - 28 minute spawn timer<BR>* Loot “Lord Bergurgle's Crown”<BR>* Give it to Shmendrik Lavawalker 3600, 0 - 15 minute spawn timer<BR>* Let Natasha Whitewater kill Shmendrik<BR>* Kill “a spirit of flame”<BR>* Loot "Damaged Goblin Crown"<BR>